snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Fans Push To Fire Amber Heard Backfires... ?!
snippet.description:
There are some who say that fans can be a bit "too attached" to celebrities that they admire. Mainly because they have "blinders on" when it comes to them and thus if they do something wrong, they try and cover for it or even straight-up deny that someone like them "couldn't possibly do that". However, when it comes to the realm of Johnny Depp and his fans, it might honestly be the opposite in terms of them being absolutely right that Johnny is incapable of what he's been accused of, and as such, they're rallying harder than ever to go and support him. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the latest fan movement that concern Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Does it surprise you that these fans are going so far to try and get Amber Heard off of Aquaman and "bring her to justice"? Do you think that things will change because of them? Or because filming on Aquaman 2 has begun that they won't be able to make an impact in time? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
